<title>DamageOnCollisionSystem</title><para>Processes <computeroutput>SolidCollisionEvent</computeroutput> and applies damage:</para>
<para>1. Reads collision events from the pass buffer 2. Checks if source entity has <computeroutput>DamageDealerComponent</computeroutput> 3. Checks if target entity has <computeroutput>HealthComponent</computeroutput> 4. Looks up damage value by target&apos;s collision layer 5. Calls <computeroutput>takeDamage()</computeroutput> on target&apos;s health component 6. Updates <computeroutput>LastAttackerComponent</computeroutput> with attack context</para>
<para>The attack source is resolved through <computeroutput>EmittedByComponent</computeroutput> if present (e.g., projectile â†’ player).</para>
